{
  "stem": "23350.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was, for her, very important.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she lit candles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the meantime, my-- my brother-in-law-- olov ha-sholom-- because he died a few years ago now.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had a fiance before the war who he wanted very much to find.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He loved his fiance very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was going from one end of Germany to-- to-- to the other end-- from the American zone to the English zone-- to find his fiance.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the end, he could see he-- it was-- there was no sign of her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he went past this point, he had to pass this side little street in-- in Germany, in Luneberg and sees candles, the light.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he knocked at the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my sister had just washed her hair, and she was wearing a scarf, was careless-- she put-- didn't know she made her hair.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It looks-- the hair was already grown.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was already quite longish by this time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when he came in, and they started talking-- and they got to like each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, he-- they decided-- he was older than her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was at an age where she could marry easily.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this is what-- when they got around, they started-- they decided to get married.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My brother-in-law is a-- was a very intelligent man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "During the war, in the ghetto, when everybody was running here, running there, he also had to do all his work, whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when he was trying to hide at night or whatever-- in the morning-- he had a violin, because he lived in the Lodz before the war.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he taught himself violin in a cellar, someone overture.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or he would teach himself English.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Hebrew-- he was a teacher of Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
